		<h2>Dropdown links</h2>
	</header>

	<p><strong>Link-triggered dropdowns</strong> are handy in navigation bars or inline contexts where the control should still behave like a link (e.g., a section title with quick actions). Knob triggers add pill styling for touch-friendly menus. Make sure anchors have <code>href</code> or <code>role="button"</code> plus keyboard handlers (Enter/Space) so activation isn’t mouse-only.</p>
  
