	<p class="note"><strong>Filtering tips:</strong> announce filter changes inline (e.g., selected count) and debounce any live queries to avoid flicker. See <a href="/documentation/elements/checkboxes-radios">Checkboxes &amp; radios</a> for input styling and accessibility guidance.</p>

